<p>
<b>MPWEMU YERA, ARI WE MPWEMU MWERANDA, ASHOBORA KUGUHA GUTSINDA KU MUSI KU 
MUSI.</b><p align="left">Ngizi ingingo zitatu zogufasha kuibitahura:</p>
    <p>1. Utarakira Yesu Kristo ngw abe Umukiza wawe, wariganza mu&nbsp; vyo 
    wakora vyose. <font color="#000080"><b>( Yes. 53:6).</b></font></p>
    <p>2. Umaze kwakira Yesu Kristo, Mpwemu Yera yaciye aba mu mutima wawe.&nbsp;
    <font color="#000080"><b>(Rom. 8:9).</b></font> </p>
    <p>3. Mpwemu Yera afasha umukristo wese kwama anezerewe. Ubwo ni bwo buginyo 
    bwuzuye umwidegemvyo. <b><font color="#000080">(2 Kor. 3: 18).</font></b></p>
    <p align="center"><b>TWITEGEREZE ICO IGITABO C'IMANA KITUBARIRA KU VYA<br>
    MPWEMU YERA.</b></p>
    <p align="left">1. Mpwemu Yera n'lmana <font color="#000080"><b>(Ivyak. 
    5:3-5).</b></font><br>
    2. Mpwemu Yem abe mu muntu wese yakiriye Yesu Kristo ngw abe Umukiza&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; wiwe. <font color="#000080"><b>(1 Kor. 3:16).</b></font><br>
    3. Mpwemu Yera n'Umwigisha wacu <font color="#000080"><b>(Yoh. 14:26).</b></font><br>
    4. Mpwemu Yera aradufasha mu ntege nke zacu <font color="#000080"><b>(Rom. 
    8:26).</b></font><br>
    5. Mpvvemu Yera afire ubushobozi gusumba izindi mpwemu zose&nbsp; <b>
    <font color="#000080">(1 Yoh.4:1-4).</font></b><br>
    6. Mpwemu Yera aduha kwame imbuto nziza mu bugingo bwacu <b>
    <font color="#000080">(Gal. 5:22,23).</font></b><br>
    7. Mpwemu Yera aduha ubushobozi bwo gushingira intahe Kristo <b>
    <font color="#000080">(Ivyak. 1:8).</font></b></p>
    <p align="left"><font color="#000080"><b>BIBILIYA ITUBWIRA IVYEREKEYE ABANTU 
    B'UBURYO BUTATU.</b></font></p>
    <p align="center"><b><font size="5">UMUNTU ATAR'UMUKRISTO</font></b></p>
    <p align="left"><b><font size="7">1</font>Uyo n'umuntu atarakira Yesu Kristo 
    ngw abe Umukiza wiwe. Mpwemu Yera&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ntaba muri we.</b></p>
    <p align="center"><b>Dusoma nmu gitabo c'Irnana ngw</b></p>
    <p align="center">Arik'umuntu afise umubiri n'ubwenge gusa, ntiyemera ivya 
    Mpwemu w'lmana, kukw ar' ubupfu kuri we, kandi ntashobora kubimenya, kuko 
    vyitegerezwa mu buryo bw impwemu <b><font color="#000080">(1 Kor. 2:14).</font></b></p>
    <p align="center"><font color="#000080"><b>Itegereze neza igicepu 
    gikurikira:</b><br>
&nbsp;</font></p>
    <p align="center"><b>Umuntu w'uburyo bwa mbere<br>
    IKI GICAPU CEREKANA INGENE UMUNTU ATARI UMUKRISTO AMERA</b></p>
    <div align="center">
      <center>
    <table border="0" width="506" cellpadding="4" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" width="210" rowspan="4">
        <img border="0" src="images/law4.1x.gif" width="192" height="171"></td>
        <td width="270" colspan="2">&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="28" valign="middle" align="center">
        <img border="0" src="images/chair5-2.gif" width="32" height="52"></td>
        <td width="230">= Intebe y inganii yo mu&nbsp; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; mutima wumuntu</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="28" valign="middle" align="center">
        <img border="0" src="images/manchair5-3.gif" width="32" height="62"></td>
        <td width="230">= Nya muntu nyene</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="28" valign="middle" align="center">
        <img border="0" src="images/cross5-4.gif" width="36" height="52"></td>
        <td width="230">= Yesu </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
      </center>
</div>
    <p dir="ltr"><b>Biraboneka neza yuko:</b><br>
    1. Yesu Kristo atari mu mutima wiwe.<br>
    2. Umuntu atari umuKristo ni we yicaye ku ntebe y'inganji mu mutima wiwe.<br>
    3. Uyo muntu akeneye kwakira Yesu Kristo ngw abe Umukiza wiwe.</p>
    <p dir="ltr" align="center"><b><font color="#000080">Umuntu 
    w'uburyo bwa kabiri ni:</font></b></p>
    <p dir="ltr" align="left"><font size="4" color="#000080"><b>UMUKRISTO YUZUYE 
    MPWEMU YERA ARI WE MPWEMU MWERANDA</b></font></p>
    <p dir="ltr" align="left"><font size="7" color="#000080"><b>2</b></font>Twakiriye 
    Yesu Kristo ngw abe Umukiza wacu, duca twuzuzwa Mpwemu <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Yera <b> <font color="#000080">(Rom. 8:9).</font></b><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; lyo twujujwe Mpwemu Yera duca twemerera 
    Yesu Kristo ngw atuganze <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; akaturongora.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Mpwemu Yera aca yama imbuto muri twebwe 
    kandi agaca aduha ubushobozi <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; bwo kwama dushingira intahe Kristo <b>
    <font color="#000080">(Ivyak. 1:8).</font></b></p>
    <p dir="ltr" align="left"><b>Dusoma mw Ijambo ry'Imana ngw</b></p>
    <p dir="ltr" align="left">Arkw ivyo Mpwemu Yera yama n'urukundo, umunezero, 
    amahoro, ukwihangana, kugira neza; ingeso nziza, kuba iumwizigirwa, 
    uburwaneza, ukwirinda: ibimeze birtyo nta vyagezwe bibibuza <b>
    <font color="#000080"><br>
    (Gal. 5:22,23).</font></b> Ariko muzohabwa ubushobozi, 
    Mpwemu Yera ni yabazako, muzoba ivyabona vyo kunshingira intahe <b>
    <font color="#000080">(Ivyak. 1:8)</font></b></p>
    <p dir="ltr" align="left"><b>Iyo twemereye Yesu Kristo kutupnza muri vyose 
    tugomba&nbsp; kwama tunezereza Imana. Urebona yuko:</b></p>
    <p dir="ltr" align="center"><br>
    <b><font color="#000080">iki gicapu kitwereka ingene umuKristo yuzuye Mpwemu 
    Yera amera</font></b></p>
    <p dir="ltr" align="center"><font size="4" color="#000080"><b>UMUKRISTO 
    YUZUYE MPWEMU YERA</b></font><b><font size="7" color="#000080"><br>
&nbsp;</font></b></p>
    <div align="center">
      <center>
<table border="0" width="782" cellpadding="4" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" width="235">
        <p align="left"><b><font size="4">Uyo Mukristo:</font></b><br>
        - ahaye Yesu Kristo intebe<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; y'inganji mu mutima wiwe<br>
        - afise ubushobozi bwa <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; Mpwemu Yera<br>
        - azana abandi kuri Yesu <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; Kristo<br>
        - asenga gushitsa aronse <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; inylshu<br>
        - yizigira Imana<br>
        - atahura Ijambo ry'Imana<br>
        - agamburukira Imana</td>
        <td align="center" width="1">
        <img border="0" src="images/law4.2x.gif" width="192" height="171"></td>
        <td align="center" width="296">
        <p align="left"><b><font size="4">Ubugingo bwiwe bwerekana</font></b><br>
        - urukundo<br>
        - umunezero<br>
        - amahoro<br>
        - ukwihangana<br>
        - ubugwaneza<br>
        - ivyizigiro<br>
        - ingeso nziza<br>
&nbsp;</td>
      </tr>
      </table>
      </center>
</div>
    <p align="left"><b>Biraboneka neza yuko:</b><br>
    1. Yesu Kristo aba mu mutima wiwe kandi ar'Umukiza wiwe. <br>
    2. Yesu Kristo ni 
    we amuganza.<br>
    3. Uyo muntu n'umusavyi agemburukira Yesu Kristo.<br>
    4. Uyo mukristo ko yemeye kurongorwa na Mpwemu Yera, imbuto za Mpwemu 
    zirongerekana muri we,&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>
    <b><font size="4">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    </font></b>kandi arakura agakomera mu bukristo.<b><font size="4"><br>
    </font>Yaman iyo umukristo atuzuye Mpwemu Yera, amere nk'uyu muntu muntu 
    w'uburyo bga gatatu.</b></p>
    <p align="left"><b><font size="7" color="#000080">3</font><font size="4">Umuntu 
    w'uburyo bwa gatatu ni:</font><font size="7" color="#000080"><br>
    </font><font size="5">UMUKRISTO YIKUNDA</font></b></p>
    <p align="left"><b>Umukristo yikunda yitwaririka ibimunezereza gusumba 
    ibinezereza Imana. Uyo mukristo ameze nk'umwana mutoyi yama agornba 
    ibimuhimbara, ameze nk'umuntu w'isi gusa.</b></p>
    <p align="left"><b>Dusoma mw Ijambo ry'Imana ngo:</b></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr">Kubganje. bene data, sinashoboye kubabwira 
    nk'ab'impwenu, ariko nababwiye nk'abaganzwa n'akameremere k'imibiri yabo, 
    nk'abana b'Inzoya bo muri Kristo. Nabaramije amata, sinabagaburiye ivyo 
    kurya bigumye: kuko mutaribgabishobore. Kandi na none ntimurabishobora. kuko 
    mukiganzwa<br>
    n'ivy' akameremere kanyu. Ko muri mwebwe har' ishari n'ugutongana, 
    ntimuganzwa na vyo? Ntimugenda nk'abantu? <b><font color="#000080">(I Ab'i 
    Korinto 3:1-3).</font></b></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr"><font color="#000080"><b>Ubu na ho ni witegereze:</b></font></p>
    <p align="center" dir="ltr"><b>iki gicapu kitwereka ingene umuKristo yikunda 
    amera. </b>
    </p>
    <p align="center" dir="ltr"><b>UMUKRISTO YIKUNDA</b><br>
    </p>
<div align="center">
  <center>
<table border="0" width="782" cellpadding="4" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" cellspacing="0">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" width="381">
        <p align="left"><font size="4"><b>Uyo Mukristo:<br>
        </b>- ntiylzigira Imana muri vyose<br>
        - kenshi na kenshi n'ikigaba<br>
        - ntafasha abandi kuza kuri Kristo<br>
        - ntashishikara gusenga<br>
        - ntagira umwete wo kwiga&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; Bibiliya<br>
        - kenshin a kenshi agira <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp; ivyiyumviro bibi.<br>
&nbsp;</font></td>
        <td align="center" width="105">
        <img border="0" src="images/law4.5x.gif" width="192" height="171"></td>
        <td width="270"><font size="4"><b>ashobora:<br>
        </b>- kugira ishari<br>
        - kugira umutima<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; umucira urubanza<br>
        - ariganyira<br>
        - arihebura<br>
        - ahinyura abandi<br>
        - arashavura<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>
&nbsp;</font></td>
      </tr>
      </table>    
    </center>
</div>
    <p align="left"><b>Nkuko nwvyiboners:<br>
    </b>1. Yesu Kristo aracari mu mutima w'uwo muntu ar' Umukiza wi we.<br>
    2. Yamara biboneka k'uwo muntu ari we yiganza. <br>
    3. Yesu Kristo ntamugenza 
    rwose muri vyose.<br>
    <b>Umukristo yikunda rimwe no rimwe aragerageza kunezereza Imana yamara uko
    <br>
    agira kwose biromwankira:</b></p>
    <p align="left"><br>
    <b>Bibiliya itubwira igituma atsindwa:</b></p>
    <p align="left">Sinzi ico nkora, kukw ico ngomba gukora atari co nkora, 
    arikw ico nanka akaba ari co nkora. Ndazi yuko muri jewe, mu kameremere 
    kanje, ata ciza kimbamwo. Kuko kugomba gukora iciza kubana nanje ariko 
    kugikora nta kwo. Ewe jewe ndagowe! Ni nde yonkiza umubiri untera uru rupfu?<br>
    <b><font color="#000080">(Rom. 7:15,18,24).</font></b></p>
    <p align="left"><font color="#000080"><b>Kubw'ivyo:</b></font></p>
    <p align="left">Umukristo yikunda ntagira umunezero mu bugingo bgiwe. Kenshi 
    na kenshi ivyaha biramunesha.<br>
    Rimwe na rimwe ntiyigenza nk'umukristo.</p>
    <p align="left"><b>Hinge twiyibutse ivyo twasomye, twongere twitegereze:</b></p>
    <p align="center">&nbsp;</p>
    <p align="center"><b><font size="4">BA BANTU B'UBURYO BUTATU</font></b></p>
    <div align="center">
      <center>
      <table border="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td width="33%">
          <p align="center">1. UMUNTU ATAR'UMUKRISTO</td>
          <td width="33%">
          <p align="center">2. UMUKRISTO YUZUYE MPWEMU YERA</td>
          <td width="34%">
          <p align="center">3. UMUKRISTO YIKUNDA</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td width="33%">
          <p align="center"><img border="0" src="images/law4.1x.gif" width="192" height="171"></td>
          <td width="33%">
          <p align="center"><img border="0" src="images/law4.2x.gif" width="192" height="171"></td>
          <td width="34%">
          <p align="center"><img border="0" src="images/law4.5x.gif" width="192" height="171"></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      </center>
</div>
    <p align="center" dir="ltr">&nbsp;None ga mugenzi, umeze nka nde mur'aba 
    bantu batatu?<br>
    Wumva wifuze kumera nka nde muri bo?</p>
    <p align="center" dir="ltr"><b>NONE UMUKRISTO YIKUNDA YOKWUZUZWA MPWEMU YERA 
    ATE?</b></p>
    <p align="center" dir="ltr"><b>TWUZUZWA MPWEMU YERA KUBWO KWIZERA</b></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr">Duhinduka abakristo iyo twizeye yuko Yesu Kristo 
    ar' Umukiza wacu. Twuzuzwa Mpwemu Yera kubgo kwizera gufatanije no kwizigira 
    Imana hamwe no kwumvira Ijambo ryayo. Woshobora kwerekanisha ukwizera kwawe 
    mu gukurikiza izi ngingo zitatu ubu nyene.</p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr">1. <b>BWIRA IMANA K'UGOMBA IJWUZUZWA MPWEMU YERA</b>
    <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hahirwa abafise inzara n'inyota vyo kugororoka, kukw ari bo 
    bazohazvva <b><font color="#000080">(Mat. 5:6). </font></b><br>
    2. <b>WATURIRE IMANA IVYAHA VYAWE.</b><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ni twetura ivyaha vyacu, ni yo yo kwizigirwe kandi igororoka 
    ivyo ni vyo bituma iduharira ivyaha&nbsp; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; vyacu ikatwoza ukugabitanya kwose <font color="#000080"><b>(I Yoh. 
    1:9).</b></font></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr"><b><font color="#000080">Kwatura ivvaha 
    bisobanurwa ko:<br>
    </font></b>a) Wemerera Imana ko wacumuye<br>
    b) Ushimira Imana ko yaguhariye, ikakwoza mu maraso ya Yesu Kristo 
    yagupfiriye ku musaraba <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; kubera ivyaha vyawe.<br>
    c) Uvuye mu vyaha vyawe, ukumvira Imana. Uko ni kwo kwihana nyakuri.<br>
&nbsp;</p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr"><b>NI WIHEREZE IMANA<br>
    </b>Kandi ntimugahe icaha imibiri yanyu ngw ikoteshwe n'ukugabitanya; ariko 
    mwishikanire Imana nk'abazuke bavuye mu bapfuye, n'imibiri yanyu muyihe 
    Imana, kugira ngw ikoreshwe no kugororoka <b><font color="#000080">(Rom. 
    6:13).</font></b></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr">Tugomvye kwuzuzwa Mpwemu Yera dukwiye kwemera Yesu 
    Kristo ngw aganze ubugingo bwacu hamwe n'ivyo dukora vyose. Ni we akwiye 
    kuganza ubutunzi bwacu arnafaranga, inka, amatongo, igihe cacu 
    c'umwidegemvyo, ibikorwa vyacu, uburyo tubana n'imiryango yacu, abagenzi 
    bacu n'abandi.</p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr"><b>None ga mugenzi, warakurikije izo ngingo 
    zitatu? <br>
    Ousubiremwo tuzisome?</b></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr"><b>UBU RERO NI WIZIGIRE KW'IMANA IKWUZUZA MPWEMU 
    YERA</b></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr">Imana ishobora kukwuzuza Mpwemu Yera ni waba 
    wizeye kwishobora kubikora.<br>
    <b>Har' ikintu bibiri bikum-bikum ukwiye kwibuka:</b></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr"><b>1. GAMBURUKIRA IBWIRIZWA RYAYO RYO KWUZURA 
    MPWEMU YERA<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>Kandi ntimukaborerwe vino irimwo ubuhumbu, ariko mwuzure 
    Mpwemu. <b><font color="#000080">(Ef. 5:18)<br>
    </font>2. NI WIZIGIRE ISEZERANO RYAYO RYO KUKWUZUZA MPWEMU YERA.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>Ubu ni bwo bushizi bw'ubwoba dufise kuri yo, n'ukw iyo 
    dusavye ikintu cose gihwanye n'ivy igomba,&nbsp; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; itwumva. Kandi ko tuzi yuko yumva ico dusavye cose, 
    bitumenyesha yuko duhawe ivyo tuyisavye <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><font color="#000080">(I Yoh. 5:14, 15).</font></b></p>
    <div align="center"><center><table border="0" cellpadding="25" width="90%">
      <tr>
        <td width="100%" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
    <p align="center" dir="ltr"><font color="#000080"><b>UBU NYENE NI WIZERA, 
    WOSHOBORA KWUZUZWA <br>
    MPWEMU YERA</b></font></p>
    <p align="center" dir="ltr">Ugusenga n'uburyo bumwe bwo kwerekana ukwizera 
    kwawe.</p>
    <p align="center" dir="ltr"><b>KUMBURE WOSHIMA GUSENGA UTI:</b></p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr">Mwami Yesu, ndagombe ko wsgwnza ubugingo bganie. 
    Namye niganza, non' ubu ndemera kw ico aekaha. Ubu rero ndacihannye 
    kandi-ndakwishikeniye, ndarneye kw ari we nzohora ngemburukira.<br>
    Ndagukengurukiye ko wampwiye ivyaha vyanj e. Ubu nemeye ibwirizwa ryawe, 
    kandi nizigiye k'ushobora kunyuzuza Mpwemu wawe Yera. Ndagukengurkiye yuk' 
    unyujuje Mpwemu nk'uko wabisezeranye.</p>
    <p align="left" dir="ltr">Mbega wumva wokwemerera Imana ngw ikwuzuze, 
    ikakuganza ikaguha ubushobozi mu bugingo bwawe?<br>
    Wumva wokwemerera kuvuga ico gisabisho ubu nyene?</p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><font color="#000080"><b>ASANGWA WIZIGIYE, WOSHOBORA 
        KUMENYA KO WUJUJWE MPWEMU YERA</b></font></p>
        <p>Mbega witeguye nk'uko twabisobanuye ku mpapuro <b>
        <font color="#000080">za 12-14?</font></b> Wumva wizigiye kw Imana 
        yashikije isezerano ryayo ryo kukwuzuza Mpwemu Yera?</p>
        <p>Iki gicapu c'umuduga cerekana ingene umuntu ashobora kwuzuzwa Mpwemu 
        Yera kubwo kwizera.</p>
        <p align="center">&nbsp;</p>
        <p align="center"><img border="0" src="images/kiru_truck.gif" width="600" height="174"></p>
        <p>1. Ukuri n'amasezerano y'Imana tubigereranya n'imoteri y'umuduga. 
        UKURI gufise <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ubushobozi bwo kuturongora. <br>
        2. Ukwizera Imana tukugereranya n'irisansi. UKWIZERA kudufatanya 
        n'UKURI.<br>
        3. Ivyiyumviro tubigereranya n'umukogote ukwegwa n'umuduga. Ni 
        twakurikiza ukuri, <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; IVYIYUMVIRO vyacu bizokurikira inzira y'ukuri.<br>
        4. Twizera Imana n'ukuri kwayo kuruta ivyiyumviro vyacu.<br>
&nbsp;</p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><b><font color="#000080">WOSHOBORA KUBANDANYA KWUZUZWA 
        MPWEMU YERA NO KUGANZWA NA WE</font></b></p>
        <p>Ni wongera gukora icaha c'ukwiganza, utegerezwa gukora ibi bintu 
        bibiri bikurikira:<br>
        1. <b>Banta wihane imbere y'lmena:</b> lzoca iguharira kandi yongere 
        ikwoze ivyaha&nbsp; <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; vyawe-<b><font color="#000080">(Yoh. 1:9).</font></b><br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Uhebe ico caha-co kwigenza.<br>
        2. <b>Uteysrezwa kwuzuzwe Mpwsm Yera, akepnzwe kandl cgskomozm no we.<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </b>Saba Umwami Yesu ngw akwiganzire muri vyose. Gamburukirs 
        ibwirizwa ry'Imana <br>
        <b><font color="#000080">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></b>ryo kwuzuzwa Mpwemu Yera <b><font color="#000080">(Ef.6:18).<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></b>Kandi wizere kw Imana ishitsa iryo sezerano <b>
        <font color="#000080">(I Yoh.5:14,15).</font></b></p>
        <p>Urama ugenza urtyo igihe core Mpwemu Yea azokwereka icaha mu bugingo 
        bwawe. Gurtyo uzoheza unezerwe, wame imbuto za Mpwemu.</p>
        <p>Ni wizera kw Imana iguma ikwujuje mur' ubwo buryo, gurtyo <br>
        Yesu Kristo azogurna ari ku ntebe y'inganji mu mutima wawe.<br>
        <font color="#000080"><b>Ushobars kumenya me ko:</b></font></p>
        <p><font color="#000080"><b>IYO URONGOWE KANDI UKAGANZWA NA MPWEMU YERA:</b></font><br>
        </p>
        <p><em style="font-style: normal">1. Ubuzima bwawe buzotera imbue mu 
        kwema imbuto ya Mpwam Yera <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <font color="#000080"><b>(Gal. 6:22.23).</b></font><br>
        2: Ammengesho yaws azogire akanaro <font color="#000080"><b>(Yak. 5:16).</b></font><br>
        3. Uzorushiriza gutshura ivyanditrvva vyera <b><font color="#000080">(2 
        Tim. 3:16).</font></b><br>
        4. Uzoronka ubushobozi bwo gushingira intahe Yesu <b>
        <font color="#000080">(Ivyak. 1:8).</font></b> <br>
        5. Imata izoguhs inkomezi zo gutsinds ibikuperogeza n'ivyaha<br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><font color="#000080">(I Kor. 10:13).</font></b><br>
        6. Uzokwama wizigira Imana n'amaaezerano-yayo <b><font color="#000080">
        (2 Pat. 1:3-11). </font></b><br>
        7. Uzobandanya kuguma wujujwe Mpwemu Yera kubgo kwizere <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <b><font color="#000080">(Heb. 11:6; I Yoh. 5:1-5).</font></b><br>
        8. Uzohabwa ubushobozi ku mpwemu zihumanye <b><font color="#000080">(1 
        Yoh. 4:1-4).</font></b></em></p>
        <p align="center"><font color="#000080"><b>Ikintu gikum rwose n'uko:</b></font><br>
        </p>
        <hr>
        <p align="center"><font color="#000080"><b>WOKWAMA UIA GUSENGA</b></font></p>
        <p align="center">Iyo igisate vy'inkwi bikomanijwe mu muriro, biraka 
        cane, ariko iyo ukuye igisate kimwve mu ziko ukagishira ukwa conyene 
        gica gitangura kuzima.<br>
        Nawe n'uko nyene, vyokugora kuba umukristo udafatanije n'abandi.<br>
        N'ikintu gikuru cane gufatanya n'abandi bakristo bakiriye Yesu Kristo 
        ngw abe Umukama wabo n'Umukiza.<br>
        Ukwiye gufatanya n'ishengero ry'abantu bemera ko Bibiliya ar'iy'ukuri, 
        kandi bakagamburukira Yesu Kristo <b><font color="#000080">(Heb. 10:25).</font></b><br>
        <br>
        <font color="#000080"><b>Asengwa ibiri mur'ako gatabo vyagufashije:</b></font></p>
